response.overview: Dubstep Dispute is a 3D animated short set in the distant future with a cast of disgruntled droids along with their vocal apartment. Driven by the sounds of electronic music, of the genre dubstep, the short takes a literal interpretation of the syncopated rhythms and aggressive sounds of dubstep and translates it to a language used by arguing robots.
response.title: Dubstep Dispute
